{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/effective-python/item_12/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hong_devlog","author":"hongdev","siteUrl":"https://hong-dev.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"hong-dev/hong-dev.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"72d63a18-4c17-5f9c-a16b-3d8a121106a5","excerpt":"Effective Python: Second Edition 내용 정리 Item 12: Avoid Striding and Slicing in a Single Expression 기본적인 striding의 문법은:  slicing과 비슷하게 start index와 end index를 입력하고, 얼마 간격으로 건너뛰기를 할 것인지 stride를 입력한다. striding(건너뛰기)은 nth번째마다 뽑아서 가져올 수 있다. slicing 할 때, striding을 사용하면 홀수번째와 짝수번째 index…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p><em>Effective Python: Second Edition 내용 정리</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"item-12-avoid-striding-and-slicing-in-a-single-expression\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#item-12-avoid-striding-and-slicing-in-a-single-expression\" aria-label=\"item 12 avoid striding and slicing in a single expression permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Item 12: Avoid Striding and Slicing in a Single Expression</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>기본적인 striding의 문법은: <code class=\"language-text\">somelist[start: end: stride]</code><br>\nslicing과 비슷하게 start index와 end index를 입력하고, 얼마 간격으로 건너뛰기를 할 것인지 stride를 입력한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>striding(건너뛰기)은 nth번째마다 뽑아서 가져올 수 있다.<br>\nslicing 할 때, striding을 사용하면 홀수번째와 짝수번째 index를 grouping 하기 쉽다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">nums <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nodds <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nevens <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>negative number도 가능하다. stride가 negative이면 뒤에서부터 거꾸로 건너뛴다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">nums <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nnums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nnums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>다만, stride syntax는 가끔 예측하지 못하는 bug를 낸다.\npython에서 글자를 reverse하는 방법중에 <code class=\"language-text\">a[::-1]</code> 이 있다.\n이 방법은 Unicode string에서도 적용되는데, unicode data가 encode된 후에 적용할 경우에는 error가 발생한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'안녕하세요'</span>\n\na<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 요세하녕안</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'안녕하세요'</span>\nb <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>encode<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'utf-8'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>decode<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'utf-8'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> UnicodeDecodeError<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'utf-8'</span> codec can't decode byte <span class=\"token number\">0x94</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> position <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> invalid start byte</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>bracket (<code class=\"language-text\">[]</code>) 안에 3개의 숫자가 들어있으면 읽기가 힘들다.\nslicing syntax에 stride part까지 추가되면 매우 복잡해진다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">x<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nx<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nx<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nx<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"advice-for-usage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#advice-for-usage\" aria-label=\"advice for usage permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Advice for usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>stride를 쓸 때는 start index와 end index 사용을 피하라.</li>\n<li>\n<p>꼭 둘 다 써야겠다면, striding 한문장, slicing 한문장 나눠서 쓰는 걸 고려하라.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">nums <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nstride_nums <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">#[1, 3, 5, 7]</span>\nslice_nums <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stride_nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nslice_nums\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><em>Reference</em></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://effectivepython.com/\"><em>Effective Python : Second Edition</em></a>  </p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"Item 12: Avoid Striding and Slicing in a Single Expression","date":"August 30, 2020","category":"[Effective Python]","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/effective-python/item_12/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/effective-python/item_11/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Item 11: Know How to Slice Sequences","category":"[Effective Python]","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/python/f-string/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"f-string `=` (python 3.8)","category":"python","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2353110810","3128451518"]}